stateDiagram-v2
    %% Feature Status State Machine

    [*] --> Init
    Init --> Researching: spec-research
    Init --> Specing: spec-requirements (behavior clear)
    Researching --> Specing: analysis complete
    Specing --> SpecApproved: readiness >= ready
    SpecApproved --> Planning: spec-plan
    Planning --> PlanApproved: tasks + gate defined
    PlanApproved --> Implementing: spec-implement
    Implementing --> Verifying: tasks complete
    Verifying --> Implementing: gate fail / reopened tasks
    Verifying --> Specing: spec drift detected
    Verifying --> Done: verdict Pass + sync complete
    Done --> [*]

    Specing --> Researching: ambiguity surfaced
    Planning --> SpecApproved: design shift needs spec change

    note right of Verifying
        harness-verify is the sole
        authority for Done.
        Post-ship sync must be
        complete before finalize.
    end note
